Loki.

307
00:26:11,009 --> 00:26:13,178
Dia ada di mana-mana, Lorelei.

308
00:26:13,386 --> 00:26:17,807
Dia mempunyai mata
dan telinga di mana-mana.

309
00:26:21,520 --> 00:26:22,646
