Bilik awak memang bagus.

450
00:36:27,750 --> 00:36:30,253
Anda singgah, ada apa?

451
00:36:32,797 --> 00:36:34,882
Saya ingin mendapatkan pendapat anda.

452
00:36:35,091 --> 00:36:37,635
Saya bercakap bagi pihak
daripada Kelab Paranormal.

453
00:36:39,178 --> 00:36:42,264
Kami ada aktiviti memburu hantu

454
00:36:42,265 --> 00:36:44,516
di bangunan sekolah terbiar.

455
00:36:44,517 --> 00:36:46,101
Kami telah berulang-alik
selama lima hari,

456
00:36:46,102 --> 00:36:47,979
