459
00:36:52,525 --> 00:36:54,901
Di sini.
Tonton ini, tonton ini.
Di sini.

460
00:36:54,902 --> 00:36:57,196
- Loki!
Jom, kita tonton.
- Sini, sini.

461
00:36:57,488 --> 00:36:59,615
Tunggu.
Di sini.

462
00:37:02,702 --> 00:37:04,828
<i>Kawan-kawan, kita di tingkat 2.</i>

463
00:37:04,829 --> 00:37:08,124
<i>Setakat ini, kami tidak melihat sebarang hantu.</i>

464
00:37:08,374 --> 00:37:10,168
