467
00:37:20,428 --> 00:37:22,597
Sial, awak dengar tak?

468
00:37:23,639 --> 00:37:25,640
Betul ke?
Awak dengar tak?

469
00:37:25,641 --> 00:37:27,225
<i>- Adakah anda mendengarnya?
