Andrew kencing sendiri!

478
00:37:49,832 --> 00:37:51,791
- Adakah anda kencing sendiri?
- Tidak boleh! Tidak boleh!

479
00:37:51,792 --> 00:37:53,376
- Andrew, awak kencing.
- Awak kejam.
Kau kejam.

480
00:37:53,377 --> 00:37:55,378
- Tidak, ia hanya basah.
- Awak kejam.
Kau kejam.

481
00:37:55,379 --> 00:37:58,049
Saya dah beritahu awak!
di sana.
Awak dengar tak?

482
00:37:58,716 --> 00:38:00,718
Begitu jelas.
Awak dengar tak?

483
00:38:02,178 --> 00:38:03,429
Betul ke?

484
00:38:04,639 --> 00:38:06,098
Betul ke?

485
00:38:09,810 --> 00:38:12,688
Sejak bila kita selesaikan
perkara paranormal?

486
00:38:13,731 --> 00:38:16,900
Ayuh, Loki.
Rosetta meminta bantuan kami.

487
00:38:16,901 --> 00:38:20,905
Tetapi kes paranormal
adalah kawasan Kelab Paranormal.

488
00:38:22,448 --> 00:38:25,742
Merekalah yang patut menyiasat
fenomena ghaib,

489
00:38:25,743 --> 00:38:27,453
