522
00:40:11,307 --> 00:40:12,892
Oh, baiklah.
Terima kasih, tuan.

523
00:40:13,017 --> 00:40:16,770
Oh, by the way, ini Loki
Mendez, presiden kelab kami.

524
00:40:16,771 --> 00:40:21,317
Loki, ini Profesor Morayta,
